---

<section aria-labelledby="value-prop-heading" class="section-alt py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h2 id="value-prop-heading" class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Why Crafting Clicks</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-600">Strategy-led, design-rich, performance-first. We ship experiences that move metrics.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200/70 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-orange-50 text-orange-600">
            <!-- target icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5">
              <path d="M12 2a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1.055a7.002 7.002 0 0 1 6.945 6.945H21a1 1 0 1 1 0 2h-1.055A7.002 7.002 0 0 1 13 19.945V21a1 1 0 1 1-2 0v-1.055A7.002 7.002 0 0 1 4.055 13H3a1 1 0 1 1 0-2h1.055A7.002 7.002 0 0 1 11 4.055V3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1Zm0 4a6 6 0 1 0 0 12A6 6 0 0 0 12 6Zm0 3a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v2h2a1 1 0 1 1 0 2h-3a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V10a1 1 0 0 1 1-1Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Strategy</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600">Positioning, roadmap, and UX strategy that align brand, product, and growth.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200/70 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-orange-50 text-orange-600">
            <!-- design-dev icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5">
              <path d="M4 5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4a1 1 0 1 1 0 2H6v12h12v-4a1 1 0 1 1 2 0v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5Zm13.707 1.293a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.414l-7 7a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-3-3a1 1 0 1 1 1.414-1.414L10 12.586l6.293-6.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 0Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Design & Development</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600">Expressive UI on a fast Astro + React foundation. Accessible, scalable, and elegant.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200/70 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-orange-50 text-orange-600">
            <!-- growth icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5">
              <path d="M3 3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a1 1 0 1 1 0 2H5v14h14v-3a1 1 0 1 1 2 0v4a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V3Zm7.293 8.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 0L14 13.586l3.293-3.293A1 1 0 0 1 18.414 10H21a1 1 0 1 1 0 2h-1.586l-3.707 3.707a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0L12 13.414l-2.293 2.293A1 1 0 0 1 8 16H3a1 1 0 1 1 0-2h4.586l1.707-1.707Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Growth</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600">CRO, SEO, and analytics that turn launches into compounding results.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


